			<intro answer1="Yes" answer2="What">Got a lot of bundles of wood headed up this way. Are you a friend of the flying bondsmen?</intro>
			<Yes>Well I've got some parcel headed here by the Freedom Train. Care to help them out?</Yes>
			<What>Never mind. Just an old woman rambling.</What>
		</dialogue>
		
	</NPC>	
